Description: PhishLens - Advanced Phishing Email Analyzer
 A Burp Suite-style local tool for analyzing phishing emails.
 Features: email parsing, SPF/DKIM/DMARC checks, IOC extraction,
 VirusTotal/AbuseIPDB integration, Claude AI analysis, bulk scanning.
 Runs a local web server accessible at http://127.0.0.1:7331
